{"tid":2098670,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"至少10校恐爆疫！男拔中小學部、海泓道油天等多校自行停課","createTime":"2020-07-07T15:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T01:34:18.000Z","uid":184261,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb1b8523cf7a63ac112b600a37938105fd7e163","tid":2098670,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"昨日中午至今，本港再新增逾10宗確診或初步確診個案，當中有部份涉及學生、教職員或學生家人染疫，包括演藝學院學生確診、拔萃男書院附屬小學有學生家長確診、油蔴地天主教小學（海泓道）有學生親友亦初步確診；至少10間學校有爆疫風險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200707/YQMFMJO57UZDONO4NCUJ4O37PY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_InOneFamily&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FYQMFMJO57UZDONO4NCUJ4O37PY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_InOneFamily%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=498a3c5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FYQMFMJO57UZDONO4NCUJ4O37PY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_InOneFamily%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b86f130f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200707/YQMFMJO57UZDONO4NCUJ4O37PY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_InOneFamily&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"600543a0f355543312ce41963327393bdd382a2f","tid":2098670,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:55:32.000Z","msg":"陳肇始：就快放暑假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44a9721598c6ef58d2b1bb97bbee6e19a2831be","tid":2098670,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:56:34.000Z","msg":"係咪有跨境支那學生 ?"},{"pid":"2350c9c0d96bfbd8c951a36a1221c34733bfc7d8","tid":2098670,"uid":27432,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,